    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We already struggled a lot on performance (OS loading) problems with Single core systems (example RH850) in previous convergence projects."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Since we are moving to Aurix which has Multiple core (i.e. TC37x has three cores), it is important to have multicore concept and implementation for China convergence platform"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Motivation of Multicore"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Speed: A computational problem can be calculated in shorter time"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Speed can be increased by parallel processing"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "But synchronization between cores have overhead"
    },
